description: This header file defines function prototypes for the Dslh Object Entity in the DSL Home Model Implementation, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: DslhCreateObjEntity
methods.description: Creates an object entity with specified container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: DslhObjeoCreate
methods.description: Creates a new instance of the Dslh Object Entity.

methods.name: DslhObjeoRemove
methods.description: Removes an instance of the Dslh Object Entity.

methods.name: DslhObjeoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the Dslh Object Entity.
